	<p>HOW TO PARTICIPATE IN THE OFFER: During the Promotion Period, you can obtain an In-Pack code (“Code”) by purchasing one of the following specially marked participating products: 64 oz. Juicy Juice® (any one (1) of the six (6) participating varieties) or 8 Pack of 6.75 oz. Juicy Juice® juice boxes (any one (1) of the four (4) participating varieties) (each, a “Participating Product”); the Code is printed inside the bottle wrap for the 64 oz. product and printed on the inside paper wrap cover of the 8 Pack card. Then, visit www.juicyjuice.com/Incredibles2, click on the Promotion link and follow the instructions to provide your name, email address and enter in three (3) In-Pack Codes to receive one (1) Fandango Promotional Code via email which will be valid for a child admission (up to $7.50 total ticket and convenience fee value) to see Incredibles 2 or any Disney movie, while supplies last. Each In-Pack Code may only be used once. In-Pack Codes have no cash value. Each Participant may submit up to twelve (12) In-Pack Codes (to submit a maximum of four (4) Offer requests) per calendar month throughout the Promotion Period. </p>
	
	<p class="no-b-margin">HOW TO ENTER THE SWEEPSTAKES: There are two (2) ways to enter the Sweepstakes. 1) Offer Redemption: Participants will automatically receive one (1) entry in the Sweepstakes random drawing after following the instructions above to complete and submit an Offer request. Entry received will be subject to verification and approval of Offer request. Entry requests via Offer redemption must be received by 04:59 p.m. ET on October 31, 2018. Or 2) Mail-in: To receive one (1) Sweepstakes entry by mail without making a purchase or submitting an Offer request, send a hand-written 3” x 5” card with your name, physical address and email address to: Juicy Juice “Incredible Family Adventure” Sweepstakes, Dept. S7563, PO Box 4006, Grand Rapids, MN 55730-4006. To receive future marketing communications from Harvest Hill Beverage Company, via email only, please hand-write “OPT-IN” on the card submitted. Limit one (1) entry per outer stamped envelope per person per day. For the avoidance of doubt, there is a maximum limit of twenty-four (24) Sweepstakes entries per person throughout the Promotion Period, regardless of method of entry. All mail-in entry requests must be postmarked by October 31, 2018 and received by November 5, 2018.</p>
	
	<p>Only one (1) e-mail address may be used by a Participant to enter the Promotion. Multiple Participants are not permitted to share the same email address. Any attempt by any Participant to obtain more than the stated number of offers requests/sweepstakes entries by using multiple/different email addresses, identities, registrations, accounts, logins, or any other methods will void that Participant’s offer requests/sweepstakes entries and that Participant may be disqualified. Suspected use of any automated or robotic system to enter is prohibited and will automatically result in disqualification, in Sponsor’s sole discretion. For the purposes of this Promotion, a “day” is a calendar day, beginning at 12:00 a.m. ET and ending at 11:59 p.m. ET, except for the first day of the Promotion Period, which shall begin at 12:00 p.m. ET, and the last day of the Promotion Period, which shall end at 04:59 p.m. ET.</p>

	<p class="no-b-margin">SWEEPSTAKES WINNER SELECTION, NOTIFICATION, AND VERIFICATION: One (1) potential grand prize winner will be selected in a random drawing of all eligible entries received, to be held on or about November 15, 2018. Drawing will be conducted by Administrator, and all decisions are final. On or about November 16, 2018, the Potential winner will be contacted by telephone, email or mail at Administrator’s discretion. If potential winner cannot be reached within three (3) days of first notification attempt, if prize or prize notification is returned as undeliverable, if potential winner rejects his/her prize, or in the event of noncompliance with these Official Rules, such prize will be forfeited and an alternate winner will be selected from all remaining eligible entries. Upon forfeiture of prize, no compensation will be given. Odds of winning the grand prize are dependent on the number of eligible Sweepstakes entries received throughout the Promotion Period. Potential grand prize winner will be required to sign and return an Affidavit of Eligibility and Liability/Publicity Release (where lawful) within five (5) days of notification that they are a potential winner. If potential grand prize winner fails to comply with these Official Rules and/or to submit the required documentation within the designated time period, he/she will automatically be disqualified and the prize may be awarded to an alternate winner.</p>
	
	<p>SWEEPSTAKES GRAND PRIZE (1): An Incredible Family Adventure, awarded in the form of a $10,000 check made payable to the winner to create an incredible family adventure of their choice or anything they choose. Approximate Retail Value (“ARV”) of grand prize: $10,000. All federal, state, and local taxes, fees, are the sole responsibility of the grand prize winner.</p>
	
	<p>SWEEPSTAKES PRIZE CONDITIONS: All prize details are at Sponsor’s sole discretion. No transfer, substitution or cash equivalent for the grand prize, in whole or in part, will be permitted except at Sponsor's sole discretion, and only then for a prize of greater or equal value determined by Sponsor. Prize award is subject to verification of eligibility and compliance with the terms of these Official Rules. The prize restrictions/conditions stated herein are not all-inclusive and may be subject to additional restrictions/conditions. Noncompliance with any of these Official Rules may result in disqualification. The grand prize will be awarded provided a sufficient number of eligible entries are received.</p>
	
	<p>FANDANGO PROMOTIONAL CODE TERMS & CONDITIONS: Fandango Promotional Code is good towards one movie ticket (up to $7.50 total ticket and convenience fee value) to see Incredibles 2 or any other Disney movie at Fandango partner theaters in the U.S. Fandango Promotional Code must be redeemed March, 31 2019 and is void if not redeemed by the expiration date. Only valid for purchase of movie tickets made at www.fandango.com/promo/juicyjuice or via the Fandango app and cannot be redeemed directly at any Fandango partner theater box office. If lost or stolen, cannot be replaced and there will be no refunds. No cash value. Not valid with any other offer. Fandango Promotional Code is valid for one-time use only. Not for resale; void if sold or exchanged. If cost of movie ticket with Fandango’s convenience fee included is more than maximum value of the Fandango Promotional Code, then user must pay the difference. Fandango Loyalty Solutions, LLC is not a sponsor or co-sponsor of this program. The redemption of Fandango Promotional Code is subject to Fandango’s Terms and Policies at www.fandango.com/terms-and-policies. All Rights Reserved.</p>
	
